<view class="page-shell"><view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px; height: {{navHeight}}px;"><view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}" mode="aspectFit" /><text>返回工作台</text></view><text>停课确认</text></view><scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height: {{navSpacer}}px;"></view><view class="content"><text class="subtitle">确认停课并通知相关学员及家长</text><view class="warning-card"><text>⚠</text><view><text>确认停课：U10基础训练班</text><text>本次操作将通知相关学员及家长，请谨慎确认</text></view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">课程信息</view><view class="course-info"><image src="{{avatar}}" mode="aspectFill" /><view><text>▣ 日期时间　2026-07-16（周四） 14:00-15:30</text><text>♙ 授课教练　陈教练</text><text>⌖ 上课场馆　浦东校区 · 2号馆</text></view></view><view class="impact-grid"><view><text>♟ 受影响学员</text><text>10人</text><text>已报名学员</text></view><view><text>◷ 是否扣课时</text><text>扣除</text><text>本次课时将扣除</text></view><view><text>↻ 补课安排</text><text>待安排</text><text>需后续安排补课</text></view></view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">停课原因</view><view class="reason-grid"><view class="{{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{reasons}}" wx:key="key" data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="selectReason"><text>○ {{item.title}}</text><text>{{item.caption}}</text></view></view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">课时处理</view><view class="option-grid three"><view class="{{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{credits}}" wx:key="key" data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="selectCredit"><text>○ {{item.title}}</text><text>{{item.caption}}</text></view></view><view class="tip">♢ 提示　如选择“扣除课时”，学员的剩余课时将相应减少1节</view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">通知范围</view><view class="option-grid three"><view class="{{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{notices}}" wx:key="key" data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="selectNotice"><text>○ {{item.title}}</text><text>{{item.caption}}</text></view></view><textarea maxlength="100" placeholder="补充说明（选填），通知时将一并告知家长..." value="{{note}}" bindinput="onNote" /></view><button class="danger-button" bindtap="confirm">⚠ 确认停课并通知</button><button class="secondary-button" bindtap="goBack">返回</button><view class="safe-space"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
